net.opentsdb.query.expression

Class UnionIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.query.expression.UnionIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITimeSyncedIterator, VariableIterator

    public class UnionIterator
extends Object
implements ITimeSyncedIterator, VariableIterator
    An iterator that computes the union of all series in the result sets. This means we match every series with it's corresponding series in the other sets. If one or more set lacks the matching series, then a null is stored and when the caller iterates over the results, the need to detect the null and substitute a fill value.
    Since:
    2.3
